<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA31">
<l>pirāṉeṉṟu nāḷum perumpulari yeṉṟuṅ</l>
<l>kurānaṟ ceḻumpōtu koṇṭu – varākat</l>
<l>taṇiyuruvaṉ pātam paṇiyumavar kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>maṇiyuruvaṅ kāṇpār makiḻntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who say ‘Lord’, daily always at great dawn,</l>
<l>those who, with the good rich buds of the Kurā[-tree] throw themselves</l>
<l>at the feet of the one with the decorative form of a boar – look! –</l>
<l>will joyfully see [his] sapphire form.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
